Regina Daniels’ brother appears to be a trouble magnet as he was accused of breaking the law in the financial hub of Nigeria.  Lawrence Daniels and the charge sheet Lawrence Daniels, the elder brother of Nollywood actress Regina Daniels, is currently being detained at the Ikoyi prison, following his arrest and arraignment at a magistrate court sitting in Igbosere. Lawrence Daniels and the charge sheet According to the charge sheet, he was arrested alongside three others, on Friday, July 26, 2019, in Lekki, for assaulting a traffic control policeman.  They were also accused of disturbing public peace by making a video of the officer and instigating the public against him. Source